<section class="faqc" data-component="faq-categorized" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <div class="faqc__inner" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <div class="faqc__header" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <p class="faqc__eyebrow" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml>FAQ</p> <h2 class="faqc__title" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml>Veelgestelde <em>vragen</em></h2> <p class="faqc__sub" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml>Staat jouw vraag er niet bij? Neem contact met ons op.</p> </div> <!-- Category tabs --> <div class="faqc__tabs" role="tablist" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <button class="faqc__tab is-active" role="tab" data-cat="general" aria-selected="true" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml>  Algemeen </button><button class="faqc__tab" role="tab" data-cat="ads" aria-selected="false" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml>  Google Ads </button><button class="faqc__tab" role="tab" data-cat="seo" aria-selected="false" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml>  SEO </button> </div> <!-- FAQ panels --> <div class="faqc__panel is-active" data-panel="general" role="tabpanel" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <details class="faqc__item" open data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <summary class="faqc__question" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> Wat kost het om met BLURR samen te werken? <svg class="faqc__chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <path d="M4 6l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="faqc__answer" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <p data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml>We werken met maandelijkse pakketten vanaf €299. Dit is exclusief advertentiebudget. Neem contact op voor een offerte op maat.</p> </div> </details><details class="faqc__item" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <summary class="faqc__question" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> Hoe snel zie ik resultaten? <svg class="faqc__chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <path d="M4 6l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="faqc__answer" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <p data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml>Eerste resultaten zijn er vaak binnen 2-4 weken. Structurele verbetering zie je na 2-3 maanden consistente optimalisatie.</p> </div> </details><details class="faqc__item" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <summary class="faqc__question" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> Kunnen jullie mijn bestaande campagnes overnemen? <svg class="faqc__chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <path d="M4 6l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="faqc__answer" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <p data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml>Ja, we doen een gratis audit en nemen je campagnes over met een naadloze overdracht.</p> </div> </details> </div><div class="faqc__panel" data-panel="ads" role="tabpanel" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <details class="faqc__item" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <summary class="faqc__question" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> Wat is een goed advertentiebudget voor Google Ads? <svg class="faqc__chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <path d="M4 6l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="faqc__answer" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <p data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml>Voor lokale bedrijven start je bij €500/maand. E-commerce werkt goed met €1500+/maand. We adviseren je graag.</p> </div> </details><details class="faqc__item" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <summary class="faqc__question" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> Wat is ROAS en hoe meten jullie dat? <svg class="faqc__chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <path d="M4 6l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="faqc__answer" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <p data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml>ROAS (Return on Ad Spend) is de verhouding tussen je omzet en advertentie-uitgaven. We meten dit via Google Analytics 4 en je conversietracking.</p> </div> </details><details class="faqc__item" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <summary class="faqc__question" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> Hoe lang duurt de opzet van een campagne? <svg class="faqc__chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <path d="M4 6l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="faqc__answer" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <p data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml>Nieuwe campagnes zijn live binnen 48-72 uur na onboarding en aanlevering van benodigde informatie.</p> </div> </details> </div><div class="faqc__panel" data-panel="seo" role="tabpanel" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <details class="faqc__item" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <summary class="faqc__question" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> Hoe lang duurt SEO? <svg class="faqc__chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <path d="M4 6l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="faqc__answer" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <p data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml>SEO is een lange termijn strategie. Eerste verbeteringen zie je na 2-3 maanden, structurele groei na 6-12 maanden.</p> </div> </details><details class="faqc__item" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <summary class="faqc__question" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> Wat zit er in een SEO pakket? <svg class="faqc__chevron" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <path d="M4 6l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml></path> </svg> </summary> <div class="faqc__answer" data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml> <p data-astro-cid-cfmuvwml>Technische audit, keyword research, on-page optimalisatie, content strategie en linkbuilding — alles op maat van jouw doelen.</p> </div> </details> </div> </div> </section>


